::Feline::

She looked at the other males, but not making eye contact. "I just 
need to know where the CR chambers are and I can set up for the 
arrival of the other bots." She looked down and rubbed her hands 
together nervously. Her tail twitched behind her and her tall, 
slender figure was tence.
